{"id":211558,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/维权网-江西访民胡金水因上访遭打压劳教（图）/","date":"2012-02-21T20:51:52Z","modified":"2012-02-21T20:51:52Z","title":"维权网 | 江西访民胡金水因上访遭打压劳教（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"> </a>（维权网信息员夏飞石报道）江西万年县胡金水因上访遭政府多方打压，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，被江西省上饶市劳动教养委员会劳教一年。劳教的理由是：非正常上访，扰乱了万年县大源镇政府的工作秩序。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">63</span><span>岁的胡金水，原是个体商户，住址：江西万年县大源镇界福村委会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">57</span><span>号。身份证号：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">362331194907134114</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡金水开始上访的原因是，胡金水在大源镇开了一间小商场，却被当地公安无故查封。胡金水为此向当地政府申请行政赔偿未果，而踏上上访之路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，胡金水在北京市最高人民法院门外，三名公安人员没有向胡金水出示任何证件，将胡金水押上车，拉到北京丰台火车站对面的乐阳旅馆小房子里，抢走胡金水的上访材料，抢走身上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">90</span><span>元人民币，带上手铐押回江西。送进万年县公安局拘留所拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天。期间吃尽苦头，受尽折磨。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，万年县大源镇政府将胡金水以“非正常上访”拘禁一个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，万年县公安以胡金水敲诈接访工作人员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>元人民币为名，将胡金水拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，江西省上饶市劳动教养委员会以胡金水经常非正常上访，向政府申请数十万人民币的巨额行政赔偿，扰乱了万年县大源镇政府的工作秩序为名，判处劳动教养一年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡金水认为自己依法行使申诉上访的权利没有错，解除劳教之后，他继续向当地政府申请行政赔偿，继续维权上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡金水电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15279327219</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lsXgB3Rq4XA/T0I5VWylLII/AAAAAAAAFX8/KbY2O0-c3Gw/s1600/%C3%A6%CB%86%C2%AA%C3%A5%E2%80%BA%C2%BEq.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320px\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lsXgB3Rq4XA/T0I5VWylLII/AAAAAAAAFX8/KbY2O0-c3Gw/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BEq.jpg\" width=\"230px\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DZ7H-QffguY/T0I5YLlNflI/AAAAAAAAFYE/D5p8nq6jP44/s1600/%C3%A6%CB%86%C2%AA%C3%A5%E2%80%BA%C2%BEb.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320px\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DZ7H-QffguY/T0I5YLlNflI/AAAAAAAAFYE/D5p8nq6jP44/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BEb.jpg\" width=\"236px\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-O1WTCP2Dpxs/T0I5byQxTPI/AAAAAAAAFYM/9HS8Iy4ZeuE/s1600/%C3%A6%CB%86%C2%AA%C3%A5%E2%80%BA%C2%BEc.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320px\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-O1WTCP2Dpxs/T0I5byQxTPI/AAAAAAAAFYM/9HS8Iy4ZeuE/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BEc.jpg\" width=\"237px\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4872554335298505789?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"ht